
Welcom to ocur.io, Ocurious, home of deed domain, where each domain has both history and art, and allows access to build and trade content.

### Grant Ownership

An NFT **deed domain** is stored in your wallet and grants you exclusive access to the domain. View the domain to see your wallet address along with all posts associated to the domain. 

### Build Domain

Select your domain and use the editor to post content. Content includes datetime, location, text, and/or images and files.

### Generate OCUR

Each deed domain has an OCUR value and rate stored in its meta properties. Select a domain to see its balance and choose when to distribute to your wallet.

OCUR can be used in the world simulation or trade it in for cash.

#### Collectible

Deed domains also include a edeemable collectible that requires $0.99 Stripe payment for shipping, be sure to include the code.

To purchase additional collectibles, use [this link](https://buy.stripe.com/fZe5nBdsearXegU5kq) to place your order, requires $19.99 Stripe payment.

*Coming soon: Same as NFT only includes a Stripe link to transfer associated property.*
